co.writepath

Class Response

  • java.lang.Object
    • co.writepath.Response

  • public class Response
extends java.lang.Object
    Response container object. Different fields are set by the server depending on the type of query. In case of error, errorCode and errorMessage are set. Please see http://www.writepath.co/en/developers
